  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Inkscape</title>

    <para>
      <application>Inkscape</application> is a what you see is what you get
      Scalable Vector Graphics editor. It is useful for creating, viewing and
      changing SVG images.
    </para>

    &lfs90_checked;

